{"type":"message","id":"b4aac05e","parentId":"ea6d49c7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:33:28.130Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Summarizing system status**\n\nI've gathered that the service is running well, and health seems okay. The watchdog log might be stale from a failed check prior to the restart. It looks like I need to summarize that the watchdog appears to have recovered after restarting. The current health is good, with the Feishu probe active. The gateway loopback is functioning on 127.0.0.1:18789, and I see the launch agent is active with PID 11862. But the watchdog log is incomplete, hanging after \"executing restart.\"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0174cf0f4855dd220169c2aebf5ab481918099326a9f77b595\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwq7DrNH9DxvSl3KwIiStWgt6FOn1-KKBxwcqvZR_n7DQULK7V99NOVYti0VSrRO7dv8kHypcVipxesjWxFkvqsetPIIivb5bmZoI5qEBBMsEtW2xyTCZ6fXrzmCODElNriyeNMacWBPVkRfXGRwF4s5-m8kL826oqi-Ro2SrHXs4PPZlzSUFmt4hF2I7GX1uWAamioVKbH-myFbGV4vTqk-emwOHYj7VxkCi06rLOuN4GgpzhmuOBLQ4Sh7wH8itwsc4N5FJmGPHvX3BVv3UEGGsYLaiKCQKlbosv0YppGdsAajm7S3RR95I60dPUNkcLOG7cxyHRI0s-S2jev9xGsjn6chTkVvmUuOALwl49qiFmtG1-tu4h9mA1-0qIOq_mVRya02XP1xwRyt-a-nxvVfM3fireoWHhui5OtzLiGEj2Pk901NKA56e71yQpG2rnSvR-iedVNJi-X_hI6fdq6XoDbOzAzWSIinhmEfWZ3LvnHtQ8xmK-s_fCciWMefhxmqK__CGI9ZOnURCEwefkY4SHtambOwRFLJv5SR5H0VY0DUHiye7NmaqJP5INcaZ229s4B3glPE5LCBaS3Kdu6dDehrq7x-C0DKERXpWyaRxyJPuEqYoxpEuvpTV9uIEU9MqEWXVizHAE6uM-UY_CKlLDiB4fpaJbIa9QgfkCE8ULjqZUmMBqdaCp8EkuWlXWoxIo-MUrL2s_bcxMlOgnbRcHRjYM7wwDtCPpeSTUlSUKrUt6hjpimaQfoN29u71AdkVHREOXi_QCNdahBuYApHHyGRTFVHF07LoDZdZ8YbMPt-WZQbDW7QhQ3v9Mj33oxjU7Bgv8OkaujNuTrGA8l70J9OppbPOfEQGtxxNAN7Z_PJWFFZHCir0kYY24vgct_-KbgziQ-kmv3aNcikZBcpXBHAKamcR8snjNllD-PaNfwaiSGDnco5PFOKiIyJKRLGSS3aEdf0R65ED7WV1b45fi0ruiWC1OcxeSv_faZb03DbZ0i0xrlh_ivbqGew4dPpFrOlLonqy82CAfsBs9qOOS9TdN_JPGaJxarBFHowgWivDxFoYgX6dcYgm57SXg0zSalK0azq6HP8I6qjf0eCf1PjlvJ8nOnXzpQf-nG2Gw-Df_tQjsEu3g2769OZLh-GH6pdVgMH-00WYGxxvuB1fCAjBf4x2CgItN_KrhPYMRdiEmznFVge3zoBsgw5Ouj3fg9xmfB3nq8uenBiohkY9mX4etdwyoB2Xn1WCenZ7LlX213lqFDIAPoYyb_ZUZ9zl0ChypvPoqukz7tSDI6JDRNgy_-ohMfztkRAFRBZlOkpu0d4AdG-8IIeBvPkeqRx8ZiarU4IjQnUP2Z4QgObLsIqfuB8Qxt130HGyTBx9vTUT-PeoGdJENblnizVWP8jcMwgaBzENceHhhRMoFg-Biw==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Summarizing system status**\\n\\nI've gathered that the service is running well, and health seems okay. The watchdog log might be stale from a failed check prior to the restart. It looks like I need to summarize that the watchdog appears to have recovered after restarting. The current health is good, with the Feishu probe active. The gateway loopback is functioning on 127.0.0.1:18789, and I see the launch agent is active with PID 11862. But the watchdog log is incomplete, hanging after \\\"executing restart.\\\"\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"看了一下，当前状态是**已恢复正常**。\n\n- **Gateway 当前健康**：`openclaw health --json` 返回 `ok: true`\n- **Feishu 探活正常**：probe `ok: true`\n- **服务状态正常**：LaunchAgent 已加载，Gateway 正在运行，PID `11862`\n- **监听地址正常**：`127.0.0.1:18789`（仅本机回环）\n- **RPC probe 正常**：`openclaw gateway status` 显示 `RPC probe: ok`\n\n今晚这轮 watchdog 的轨迹大概是：\n- `23:18:22` 首次检查失败\n- 等待 30 秒后再次失败\n- 进入重启流程\n- `23:27` 左右从主日志看，Gateway 已重新拉起\n- 现在 `23:32` 再查时整体已经恢复健康\n\n补充一点：\n- `/tmp/openclaw-watchdog.log` 目前只写到 “Second failure - executing restart...”，**重启后的成功结果没有继续落盘**\n- 但主日志和实时健康检查都表明：**重启实际成功了，系统当前是活的**\n\n结论：\n**本次 watchdog 触发过一次异常并执行了自动重启；当前 OpenClaw 已恢复正常，无需额外告警。**\n\n建议后续排一下：\n1. watchdog 重启后的“成功/失败收尾日志”为什么没写完整\n2. 23:18 那次初始失败的直接原因（是临时探针失败，还是网关短暂卡死）","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0174cf0f4855dd220169c2aec34ee08191a2fd2b483367fc75\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":29625,"output":464,"cacheRead":20096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50185,"cost":{"input":0.0740625,"output":0.00696,"cacheRead":0.005024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0860465}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":17743663963